## Plans & Entitlements — Single Source of Truth

### Architecture
- **Canonical source:** `packages/shared/src/plan.ts` — ALL plan definitions, feature gates, and quotas live here
- **Backend enforcement:** `apps/api/src/utils/plan-gating.ts` → `requirePlanFeature(feature)` middleware + `requireAiQuota` middleware
- **Backend metering:** `apps/api/src/utils/entitlements.ts` — consumes shared `PLAN_AI_LIMITS` and `PLAN_M3_LIMITS`
- **Frontend hook:** `apps/web/src/hooks/useFeatureAccess.ts` → `useFeatureAccess()` hook returns `can(feature)` 
- **Frontend fetch:** `apps/web/src/lib/org-features.ts` → `fetchOrgFeatures()` with 30s cache
- **API endpoint:** `GET /portal/org/features` — returns `{ planKey, features: Record<FeatureKey, boolean>, minPlan }`
- **Stripe webhook:** `apps/api/src/routes/stripe-webhook.ts` — uses `getAiLimitForPlan()` from shared for instant limit sync

### Plan Limits
| | Free | Starter | Pro | Business |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Agents | 3 | 5 | 15 | 50 |
| Conversations/mo | Unlimited | Unlimited | Unlimited | Unlimited |
| AI messages/mo | 200 | 500 | 2,000 | Unlimited |
| Branding | Required | Removable | Removable | Removable |
| File upload | Yes | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| Languages | All free | All free | All free | All free |
| API access | — | — | — | Business |

### Feature Tiers (from FEATURE_MIN_PLAN)
- **Free:** ai_inbox, ai_config, billing_checkout, billing_portal, file_sharing
- **Starter:** auto_reply, working_hours, read_receipts, transcript_email, workflows, macros, remove_branding
- **Pro:** ai_persona, ai_suggestions, custom_css, page_rules, pre_chat_form, csat, white_label, audit_log
- **Business:** priority_support, sla, custom_domains, api_keys

### Rules for Adding New Plan-Gated Features
1. Add FeatureKey to `packages/shared/src/plan.ts` → `FEATURE_MIN_PLAN`
2. Add `requirePlanFeature("feature_key")` to API route preHandler
3. Frontend: use `useFeatureAccess()` → `can("feature_key")` for UI gating
4. **NEVER** hardcode plan checks (e.g. `planKey === "pro"`) — always use shared functions

